    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The condition or quality of not depending on another, as applied to a political entity, other group, or an individual. Includes the exemption from external control or support, freedom from subjection, or from the influence of others, and individual liberty of thought or action.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
